  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a few days, my mom said-- my mom said, we like the baby so much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stay there till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can stay as well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish baby.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Fritz did part of duties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave the bottle, and whatever that he could do, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister bleached the baby's hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was black.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we told the neighborhood that one them, my aunt was-- had TB, and was in the hospital, and asked us to look after the baby till she was back out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my sister walk around with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was like a normal baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With dyed hair.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the train, and the-- the girl I had with me, and there was even a German soldier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He looked at it for a cute baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody on the train said it looked like me, the father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another said it looked like the girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It looked like the mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had [INAUDIBLE] was arrested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents encouraged me to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never-- we were-- we were scared, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] just got normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they encouraged me to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course you were in danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they never-- they never had somebody who searched the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they never had a suspicion that they were involved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only when I was interrogated by the Gestapo when I was arrested, he tried to blackmail me more or less to tell me that my father was also arrested.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was [INAUDIBLE] for that, because I took my own responsibility for that, my parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, your father's arrested, he said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said he's in same prison where I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I-- a couple of days later, because I was very afraid of that, a couple days later I got a parcel through the Red Cross from home.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the handwriting of the parcel is my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that way I could play with the Germans, and acted if it was-- that I believed that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I knew it was not true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
